body:
Does anvil retry on timeouts? Or is it just on rate limits? Possible to change the branch where if the request times out, we retry some number of times?

@mattsse Do you know if something like this would help?

```
-        let client = reqwest::Client::builder().timeout(timeout).build()?;
+        let client = reqwest::Client::builder().timeout(timeout).timeout_retry_times(5).build()?;
```

^ don't think that method exists, but basically any variation of retry on timeout.
